| logical_plan  | Sort: revenue DESC NULLS FIRST, orders.o_orderdate ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |   Projection: lineitem.l_orderkey, sum(lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - lineitem.l_discount) AS revenue, orders.o_orderdate, orders.o_shippriority                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |     Aggregate: groupBy=[[lineitem.l_orderkey, orders.o_orderdate, orders.o_shippriority]], aggr=[[sum(lineitem.l_extendedprice * (Decimal128(Some(1),20,0) - lineitem.l_discount)) AS sum(lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - lineitem.l_discount)]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |       Projection: orders.o_orderdate, orders.o_shippriority, lineitem.l_orderkey, lineitem.l_extendedprice, lineitem.l_discount                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |         Inner Join: orders.o_orderkey = lineitem.l_orderkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |           Projection: orders.o_orderkey, orders.o_orderdate, orders.o_shippriority                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |             Inner Join: customer.c_custkey = orders.o_custkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |               Projection: customer.c_custkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |                 BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |                   Filter: customer.c_mktsegment = LargeUtf8("BUILDING")                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |                     TableScan: customer projection=[c_custkey, c_mktsegment], partial_filters=[customer.c_mktsegment = LargeUtf8("BUILDING")]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |               BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |                 Filter: orders.o_orderdate < TimestampNanosecond(795225600000000000, None)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |                   TableScan: orders projection=[o_orderkey, o_custkey, o_orderdate, o_shippriority], partial_filters=[orders.o_orderdate < TimestampNanosecond(795225600000000000, None)]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |           Projection: lineitem.l_orderkey, lineitem.l_extendedprice, lineitem.l_discount                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |             BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |               Filter: lineitem.l_shipdate > TimestampNanosecond(795225600000000000, None)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |                 TableScan: lineitem projection=[l_orderkey, l_extendedprice, l_discount, l_shipdate], partial_filters=[lineitem.l_shipdate > TimestampNanosecond(795225600000000000, None)]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [revenue@1 DESC, o_orderdate@2 ASC NULLS LAST], fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
